      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attacker IP:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;10.10.10.2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Target Machine IP:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;10.10.10.28&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The objective was to enumerate the target machine, identify exposed services, gain initial access through a web backdoor and leaked credentials, then escalate privileges through a vulnerable SUID binary.&lt;/p&gt;
